## Review Scope

{{ review_scope | default("full") }}

**Named scopes** (defaults to `full` if not specified):

- `full` -- evaluate all seven dimensions (FD1-FD7).
- `adapter_pr` -- focus on FD1 (Layering) + FD2 (A-rules) + FD3 (Security) + FD6 (Tests/conformance) + FD7 (Anti-Patterns). Use for any PR that adds or modifies a file under `frontend/lib/adapters/`.
- `ui_component_pr` -- focus on FD2 (U-rules + S-rules) + FD3 (Security/sandboxing) + FD4 (Accessibility) + FD5 (Performance/streaming) + FD7 (Anti-Patterns). Use for any PR that adds or modifies a file under `frontend/components/` or `frontend/app/`.
- `wire_translator_pr` -- focus on FD2 (W-rules + T-rules) + FD6 (wire schema drift). Use for any PR that adds or modifies a file under `frontend/lib/wire/`, `frontend/lib/trust-view/`, or `frontend/lib/translators/`.
- `security_audit` -- FD3 + FD7 only. Use for security-targeted reviews.

